Motorists and pedestrians should follow posted detour signs along city streets to guide them through the area and to the Metro-North train station. Train commuters please note that Station Place will be open between Atlantic Street and the parking garage but through-traffic to/from Washington Boulevard will not be permitted. Motorists are advised to remain alert drive cautiously and to maintain a safe speed when driving in this vicinity.
